{"questionId":"24561226","questionHtml":"<p>Show that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>attempts to use the product rule to find <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempts to use the chain rule to find <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mfenced><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mfenced><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></msup><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>AG</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>attempts to find&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"htt